item.title: Vibes
item.description: There was a theme and set of topics set for this month that had to be scrapped, so this post will touch on some other stuff to keep the monthly train going - and hopefully let off some real steam on the outside. Got back into reading for the habit more than the learning. I try to do it first thing everyday while it’s still dark. It sets such a good tone for the day.
